# Sawae Brands Limited Logo

## Instructions:
1. Upload the SAWAE BRANDS LIMITED logo image to this directory
2. Recommended format: PNG or SVG
3. Recommended size: 400x400px or higher (for retina displays use 800x800px)
4. File name: `sawae-brands-logo.png` or `sawae-brands-logo.svg`

## Current Logo URL:
The logo image should be placed at: `/images/vendors/sawae-brands-logo.png`

Once uploaded, update the vendor data files:
- `src/data/mockVendors.ts` - Update logo field
- `src/data/transformed/vendors.ts` - Update logo_url field
